n<br />\n第一<br />\n你要諗嘅係<br />\n咩人先會做呢類低端工業<br />\n答案就係相對學識較低/出身背景較差嘅人<br />\n原因：讀得成書嘅 出身見得下人嘅 都唔會做工程<br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n你要諗嘅係<br />\n呢類人要繁殖 要結婚的話<br />\n對象係有咩人可以揀<br />\n答案就係支那女人/ 同等出身嘅人<br />\n原因：公屋妹都想嫁比我呢啲私樓仔啦<br />\n<br />\n所以自然<br />\n新聞一報得 <br />\n呢類人本質上住天水圍/大陸老婆/ 窮困<br />\n根本就係極大機率嘅事<br />\n當中係可以有科學解釋<br />\n<br />\n我見你第二句就提「剋夫」「降頭」<br />\n呢類極不科學嘅名詞<br />\n我建議你呢啲柒頭<br />\n唔好咁迷信啦<br />\n多啲用柒腦思考啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194500062af350c43a74241cea128839ebedf2b2","tid":2449644,"uid":262183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"161690cf0cc610b1c571567ed8a2a4b950e4b59c","tid":2449644,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"031b3005f739460104e82c48f3edcf0254ad85ba","tid":2449644,"uid":55386,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:16:50.000Z","msg":"本身打算話分佢老公死果間公屋比佢<br />\n<br />\n諗諗下無謂益佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T01:01:29.000Z","msg":"果度好似係居屋黎，山麗苑？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T01:04:46.000Z","msg":"有公屋，皇后山邨<br />\n再入先係居屋"},{"pid":"8db78c16dc2839c556a04ddd2013b29db5eb3123","tid":2449644,"uid":348176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T01:05:34.000Z","msg":"大陸婆：暫時不知他出事原因<br />\n但唔理喇比間公屋我先"},{"pid":"e40df54ff4a3727d35adb882cceedc20eb5708ec","tid":2449644,"uid":48500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T01:06:36.000Z","msg":"即刻去拎遺產"},{"pid":"ed990eeed86fc6134cc288b7a49caa8fb870f119","tid":2449644,"uid":267225,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"74a8ac7fbb60aef4943b36f0357dea43a59227fb","tid":2449644,"uid":11291,"like":271,"dislike":6,"score":265,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:12:42.000Z","msg":"即刻開口話要公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0